profile:
DESIGN MAINTENANCE IRRIGATION STRATA SERVICES

Welcome to Frascape Landscaping serving greater Victoria since 2003 and in operation since the early 1980’s. 

Frascape was one of the first to provide commercial and residential landscape services with a focus on protecting the environment by taking an “organic” approach. 

Frascape’s goal is to provide its service in the most safe and efficient manner protecting human health and the environment.

Frascape performs regular landscape maintenance, new landscape installation, and rejuvenates old landscapes. CONTRACTED STRATA SERVICES A SPECIALTY

Frascape provides a comprehensive irrigation service, employing the latest technology to ensure efficient and effective watering practices that meet and often exceed those required by regulation.
name: Frascape Landscaping    No Longer In Business
